### Index of statistics endpoints (JSON)
GET {{host}}/api/stats
Accept: application/json

### List top genres (default limit=100)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/genres
Accept: application/json

### List top genres with limit
GET {{host}}/api/stats/genres?limit=50
Accept: application/json

### List top categories (default limit=100)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/categories
Accept: application/json

### List top categories with limit
GET {{host}}/api/stats/categories?limit=50
Accept: application/json

### Review buckets (log-space default)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/reviews/buckets
Accept: application/json

### Review buckets (equal-width)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/reviews/buckets?mode=EQUAL_WIDTH
Accept: application/json

### Review buckets (equal-count)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/reviews/buckets?mode=EQUAL_COUNT
Accept: application/json

### Review buckets (linear winsorized)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/reviews/buckets?mode=LINEAR_WINSORIZED
Accept: application/json

### User achievements (all-time, default)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/users/achievements
Accept: application/json

### User achievements (all-time, explicit)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/users/achievements?timeframe=all
Accept: application/json

### User achievements (weekly - last 7 days)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/users/achievements?timeframe=weekly
Accept: application/json

### User achievements (daily - today only)
GET {{host}}/api/stats/users/achievements?timeframe=daily
Accept: application/json
